{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_SetShootable}}
'''A_SetShootable'''

(no parameters)


Makes the calling actor shootable by clearing the {{Flag|NONSHOOTABLE}} flag and setting the {{Flag|SHOOTABLE}} flag instead.

